openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Fruits

paths:

      type: object
      properties:
        fruitType:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/FruitType'
    FruitType:
      type: string
      default: PEAR
      enum:
        - APPLE
        - PEAR
    FruitWithEnum:
      required:
        - fruit
        - amount
      type: object
      properties:
        fruit:
          type: string
        amount:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        fruitType:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/FruitType'
